{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM04_ST3_620.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x13,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Whoa! That's such a big bud..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x185,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "When my grandpa was a kid, his grandpa told him..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x186,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "That even back then, it was always a huge bud."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Then, maybe it's been like this for about a hundred years..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x187,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Isn't it marvelous? It doesn't look like it's withered at all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "It looks just like the flower in the book... I wonder how I can get it to bloom..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I asked my grandpa, and he said this flower lives a really, really long time..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "And like you said, it only blooms once every hundred years."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "So for a hundred years, this plant stores up nutrients, preparing for the flower to bloom..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "And when the time is right, its flower blooms for a few days. But, it's been a looong time since its last bloom."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "My grandpa hasn't even seen it bloom."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I see... Maybe that's because this area has become a wasteland..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "In that case...if I give it some nutrients, maybe this flower will bloom!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x129,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, Ayesha, that's gotta be it!<CR>I feel like that'll do the trick!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x12b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But, how do you prepare a hundred years' worth of nutrients?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I think I can do it by synthesizing something with plenty of nutrients...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Really!? You know, I'm starting to get really excited now, too!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "You just might be the only person who can make this flower bloom..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "All right...I'm gonna do this!"
        }
    ]
}